--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

   _ _
  | (_)_   __  This file lists changes made to the Ansible role.
  | | \ \ / /  The content is sorted in reverse chronological
  | | |\ V /   order and formatted to allow easy grepping by
  |_|_| \_/    scripts.


 The fields are:
 B: bug                    I: improvement            F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 1.0.1 (2017-08-06)
I: Revise Ansible tags

* Version 1.0.0 (2017-08-01)
I: Stabilize, improve and cleanup Ansible role

* Version 0.9.0 (2017-04-16)
F: Add support for OpenBSD 6.1
F: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.0

* Version 0.8.0 (2016-10-14)
F: Add support for FreeBSD 11.0-RELEASE
F: Drop support for FreeBSD 10.3-RELEASE

* Version 0.7.0 (2016-09-03)
F: Add support for OpenBSD 6.0
F: Drop support for OpenBSD 5.9

* Version 0.6.2 (2016-05-29)
I: Improve FreeBSD support

* Version 0.6.1 (2016-05-27)
I: Improve packaging tasks

* Version 0.6.0 (2016-05-21)
F: Add support for Ansible 2.0

* Version 0.5.1 (2016-04-15)
I: Improve 'all' 'group' and 'host' options

* Version 0.5.0 (2016-04-09)
F: Add support for FreeBSD 10.3-RELEASE
F: Drop support for FreeBSD 10.2-RELEASE

* Version 0.4.0 (2016-04-02)
F: Add support for OpenBSD 5.9
F: Drop support for OpenBSD 5.8

* Version 0.3.0 (2016-03-02)
F: Add support for OS family 'OpenBSD'

* Version 0.2.0 (2016-01-21)
F: Drop support for OS family 'Gentoo'

* Version 0.1.3 (2015-11-17)
I: Add missing Ansible tags

* Version 0.1.2 (2015-11-08)
I: Improve 'group_vars' and 'host_vars' options

* Version 0.1.1 (2014-12-22)
I: Various small Ansible and Jinja2 improvements

* Version 0.1.0 (2014-12-10)
F: Initial release
